00:22:30.780 --> 00:22:35.730
The central banks are
central to commercial banks.

00:22:35.730 --> 00:22:41.490
And what's important to
remember is our money system

00:22:41.490 --> 00:22:47.670
has moved on from being
paper money to basically

00:22:47.670 --> 00:22:49.050
digital money.

00:22:49.050 --> 00:22:51.360
And so today in the
US, if you think

00:22:51.360 --> 00:22:54.450
about the total
stock of currency,

