dollars, or SunTrust dollars,

00:23:58.660 --> 00:24:00.580
or Community Bank dollar.

00:24:00.580 --> 00:24:03.740
That's what we're spending
when we walk into Starbucks.

00:24:03.740 --> 00:24:07.010
It might have some implicit
or explicit guarantee

00:24:07.010 --> 00:24:11.440
of a government here in the US,
deposit insurance and the like.

00:24:11.440 --> 00:24:14.140
But we're in essence saying
to Bank of America, please

00:24:14.140 --> 00:24:17.110
change my ledger
balance and move

00:24:17.110 --> 00:24:19.570
something to somebody
else's ledger balance,

00:24:19.570 --> 00:24:24.460
