for that local Starbucks.

00:24:24.460 --> 00:24:27.550
So in between has to be
some electronic means,

00:24:27.550 --> 00:24:31.210
some payments system, a
deferred net settlement system.

00:24:31.210 --> 00:24:34.390
And this chart lists
