00:24:43.200 --> 00:24:47.640
like the US Federal Reserve runs
something called the Fedwire.

00:24:47.640 --> 00:24:55.180
But some are run by a consortium
of the commercial banks.

00:24:55.180 --> 00:24:57.090
Some are private.

00:24:57.090 --> 00:24:59.920
And in some countries, they
can even be for-profit.

00:24:59.920 --> 00:25:03.040
But all of them
have some regulation

00:25:03.040 --> 00:25:04.160
