00:41:13.620 --> 00:41:16.530
Venmo is a form of
account to account

00:41:16.530 --> 00:41:19.800
transfer, your
account at your bank

00:41:19.800 --> 00:41:21.150
to somebody else's account.

00:41:21.150 --> 00:41:25.170
And account to account transfers
are a very important feature

00:41:25.170 --> 00:41:26.730
of the competition.

00:41:26.730 --> 00:41:28.980
But still, Venmo is not
going to move $1 million

00:41:28.980 --> 00:41:33.070
without having additional
security checks.

00:41:33.070 --> 00:41:37.655
So that's probably what's
happening here, I fear to say.

