00:48:10.630 --> 00:48:13.870
one waterworks company
per city because

00:48:13.870 --> 00:48:16.630
of that incredible network
effect of the plumbing.

00:48:16.630 --> 00:48:18.350
Similar here.

00:48:18.350 --> 00:48:20.440
